You wonder idly who left that here. You can make out a table. What a coincidence, weren't you just thinking about a table? The table is massive. On the table you can see a cookbook. You lean against the wall, inadvertently pressing a secret button. The wall opens up to reveal a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can see a sliced banana. You can make out a stove. But the thing is empty.

There is an open plain door leading north. There is an exit to the south.
